“等疫情结束，我带你去吃你最爱的火锅”。
"When the epidemic is over, I will take you to your favorite pot."
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 李文姬2月10日起，闵敏在医院发热病人隔离病区进行护理工作。
Peng Pai journalist Li Wenji February 10, Minmin in the hospital febrile patient isolation area for nursing work.
本文图片 三峡大学附属仁和医院提供“15天前，当你告诉我，你已主动报名参加抗击新冠肺炎一线、要去隔离病房工作的时候，我的心情好复杂，这是这段时间以来最害怕你说出口的事……这半月里，除了对你牵挂和担心，更因你的坚持和勇敢感到骄傲和自豪。
"Fifteen days ago, when you told me that you had volunteered to join the fight against SARS and work in the isolation ward, I was in a very complicated mood. This is the last time I feared you would say so.
”农历二月初二，何军波给在抗疫一线的妻子隔空寄出一封“情书”。
On the second day of the second month of the lunar calendar, He Junbo sent a Love Letter to his wife, who was on the frontline of the epidemic.
何军波是宜昌市高新区生物产业园石花山村村务工作者，从1月23日开始驻村抗疫。
He Junbo, a village worker in Shihua Mountain Village of Yichang Hi-tech District, started to fight the disease in the village on January 23.
他的妻子闵敏是三峡大学附属仁和医院骨科的一名护士。
His wife Minmin is an orthopaedic nurse attached to Three Gorges University.
2月10日起，闵敏就在医院发热病人隔离病区进行护理工作。
From February 10, Minmin began nursing work in the isolation ward of febrile patients in the hospital.
夫妻俩前后脚上前线，已经一个多月没见上面，每天一家人最期待的就是视频连线的“团聚”时刻。
The couple have been on the front lines for more than a month now, and the family's main daily expectation is the reunion of the video link.
闵敏会给丈夫指指脸上护目镜和口罩留下的红色压痕，也会告诉他，看到病人逐渐康复，所有辛苦都值得。
Minmin would point to the red pressure marks left by the goggles and masks on her face and tell him that it was worth all the hard work to see the patient gradually recover.
这让何军波既心疼、担忧，又由衷地骄傲。
This makes He Junbo both distressed, worried, and sincerely proud.
征得本人同意后，澎湃新闻刊载此信。
With my consent, the letter appeared in the surging news.
视频时，闵敏给丈夫指指脸上护目镜和口罩留下的压痕。
During the video, Minmin points to the pressure marks left by the goggles and mask on her husband's face.
亲爱的老婆：今天是农历二月初二。
Dear wife, Today is the second day of the second month of the lunar calendar.
老人说，“二月二，龙抬头”，相传在惊蛰前后，百虫蠢动，疫病易生，人们祈望龙抬头出来镇住毒虫。
The old man said, "February 2, dragon head up," legend before and after stinging, Zheng stupidity, disease easy to come out, people pray for dragon head up to control the insects.
今天也是你赴往“抗疫”一线的第15天，我们已经有1个月没见面了。
Today is also the 15th day of your journey to the "fight against plague," we have not seen each other for a month.
期待疫情早日结束，我带你去吃你爱吃的火锅。
Looking forward to the end of the epidemic, I will take you to eat your favorite hot pot.
15天前，当你告诉我，你已主动报名参加抗击新冠肺炎一线、要去隔离病房工作的时候，我的心情好复杂，这是这段时间以来最害怕你说出口的事。
Fifteen days ago, when you told me that you had volunteered for the first line of battle against pneumonia and were going to work in the isolation ward, I was in a very mixed mood.
作为丈夫，我自然是不愿意你去，因为我们都不知道前路有多凶险；做为一名基层工作者，我已投入防疫工作，了解其中的辛苦和不易；但作为一名党员，面对同样是党员的你，我必须支持你的决定！所以，即使曾试图说服你放弃报名，但是你说：“我们护士长和我年纪相仿，有家庭也有宝宝，她第一个就报名了！如果大家都不去，那新成立的发热病区工作怎么开展？你从大年三十回村驻守，尽职尽责，我也应该贡献我的一份光和热。
As a husband, I naturally do not want you to go, because we do not know how dangerous the road ahead is; as a grass-roots worker, I have to support your decision as a Party member.
”你的话我却无言以对，同时让我内心感到惭愧：曾经极力推荐你写下入党申请书的是我，现在阻碍你火线冲锋的也是我。
Your words left me speechless and ashamed of myself: I was the one who recommended you to write down your application for membership, and it is I who now stand in your way.
自从2月10日你进入发热隔离病区工作以后，我跟宝宝每天都期待与你视频连线的“团聚”时刻。
My baby and I have been expecting a "reunion" with your video connection every day since February 10, when you went to work in a febrile quarantine area.
“吃得怎么样？按时休息，注意保暖，调整心态，专注工作……”这是我每次结束聊天之前不厌其烦的叮嘱，我的碎碎念只是希望你平安回来。
"How's it going? Rest on time, watch your warmth, adjust your mind, focus on your job..." That's what I never tire of telling you before I end my conversation.
视频电话的时候，当你指给我看脸上护目镜和口罩留下的红红的压痕，让我心疼不已。
Video phone time, when you show me the face goggles and masks left by the red indentation, let me heartache.
现在我每天都期待接到你的电话，想知道你今天的工作是否顺利，吃睡都好不好。
Now I'm looking forward to hearing from you every day, wondering if your work today is going well and eating and sleeping well.
我记得以前我当兵出海战备值班时，要切断所有联系，值班结束第一件事就是打电话给你。
I remember when I was on military duty, I had to cut off all contact and call you the first thing after duty.
你每次接到我电话时的那份期待和欣喜，曾经的我体会不到，而现在，我深切体会到了。
Every time you receive my phone call that look and rejoice, once I did not know, but now, I deeply feel.
何军波、闵敏和他们的女儿。
He Junbo, Minmin and their daughter.
“刚开始穿防护服的时候还有一点害怕，当我进去后看到病人们渴望的眼神，更加坚信我的选择没有错！当我看到病人经过我们的治疗和护理逐渐康复，让我觉得所有的辛苦都值得！”听到你说这些，由衷地为你感到高兴。
"It was a little scary at first, but when I went in and saw the patient's eager eyes, I was more confident that my choice was right! When I saw the patient recovering from our treatment and care, it was worth all the pain!
这半月里，除了对你牵挂和担心，更因你的坚持和勇敢感到骄傲和自豪。
This half month, in addition to you worried and worried, but also because of your persistence and courage proud and proud.
此刻，你在病房与疫魔搏斗，我在村里守卫百姓平安。
At this moment, you are fighting the plague in the ward, I guard the people in the village safe.
虽然没有彼此陪伴，但我相信此时的分隔是为了他日更美好的相聚和相守。
Although not accompanied by each other, but I believe that this time of separation for his better day together and together.
等宝宝长大，我们就告诉她：2020年的新冠肺炎防疫阻击战，爸爸妈妈都是一线最勇敢的战士。
When the baby grew up, we told her: 2020 the new crown pneumonia vaccination campaign, parents are the first line of the most courageous fighters.
本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
This issue editor Chang Chen recommended reading.
